quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  37,83,"w'inn min ashyae nuh ealaa mnhajh wmllath nby allah 'ibrahym, hin ja' rabah biqalb bari' min kuli aetqad batl wkhuluq dhmym, hin qal li'abih waqawmih mnkrana elyhm: ma aldhy tebdwnh min dun allh? 'aturidun alihatan mkhtlaqat tebdwnha, wttrkwn eibadat allah almsthq llebadt whdh? fama zanukum birabi alealamin 'anah faeil bikum 'iidha 'ashraktum bih webdtm maeah ghyrh?"
  37,84,"w'inn min ashyae nuh ealaa mnhajh wmllath nby allah 'ibrahym, hin ja' rabah biqalb bari' min kuli aetqad batl wkhuluq dhmym, hin qal li'abih waqawmih mnkrana elyhm: ma aldhy tebdwnh min dun allh? 'aturidun alihatan mkhtlaqat tebdwnha, wttrkwn eibadat allah almsthq llebadt whdh? fama zanukum birabi alealamin 'anah faeil bikum 'iidha 'ashraktum bih webdtm maeah ghyrh?"
  37,85,"w'inn min ashyae nuh ealaa mnhajh wmllath nby allah 'ibrahym, hin ja' rabah biqalb bari' min kuli aetqad batl wkhuluq dhmym, hin qal li'abih waqawmih mnkrana elyhm: ma aldhy tebdwnh min dun allh? 'aturidun alihatan mkhtlaqat tebdwnha, wttrkwn eibadat allah almsthq llebadt whdh? fama zanukum birabi alealamin 'anah faeil bikum 'iidha 'ashraktum bih webdtm maeah ghyrh?"
  37,86,"w'inn min ashyae nuh ealaa mnhajh wmllath nby allah 'ibrahym, hin ja' rabah biqalb bari' min kuli aetqad batl wkhuluq dhmym, hin qal li'abih waqawmih mnkrana elyhm: ma aldhy tebdwnh min dun allh? 'aturidun alihatan mkhtlaqat tebdwnha, wttrkwn eibadat allah almsthq llebadt whdh? fama zanukum birabi alealamin 'anah faeil bikum 'iidha 'ashraktum bih webdtm maeah ghyrh?"
  37,87,"w'inn min ashyae nuh ealaa mnhajh wmllath nby allah 'ibrahym, hin ja' rabah biqalb bari' min kuli aetqad batl wkhuluq dhmym, hin qal li'abih waqawmih mnkrana elyhm: ma aldhy tebdwnh min dun allh? 'aturidun alihatan mkhtlaqat tebdwnha, wttrkwn eibadat allah almsthq llebadt whdh? fama zanukum birabi alealamin 'anah faeil bikum 'iidha 'ashraktum bih webdtm maeah ghyrh?"
  37,88,"fnzr 'iibrahim nazratan fi alnujum mtfkrana fima yaetadhir bih ean alkhuruj maeahum 'iilaa aeyadhm, faqal lhm: 'iiniy mryd. whdha taerid mnh. ftrkwh wara' zhwrhm"
  37,89,"fnzr 'iibrahim nazratan fi alnujum mtfkrana fima yaetadhir bih ean alkhuruj maeahum 'iilaa aeyadhm, faqal lhm: 'iiniy mryd. whdha taerid mnh. ftrkwh wara' zhwrhm"
  37,90,"fnzr 'iibrahim nazratan fi alnujum mtfkrana fima yaetadhir bih ean alkhuruj maeahum 'iilaa aeyadhm, faqal lhm: 'iiniy mryd. whdha taerid mnh. ftrkwh wara' zhwrhm"
  37,91,"fmal msreana 'iilaa 'asnam qawmih faqal msthzyana bha: 'ala takulun hdha altaeam aldhy yuqadimuh lakum sdntkm? ma lakum la tantiqun wala tjybwn man ysalkm?"
  37,92,"fmal msreana 'iilaa 'asnam qawmih faqal msthzyana bha: 'ala takulun hdha altaeam aldhy yuqadimuh lakum sdntkm? ma lakum la tantiqun wala tjybwn man ysalkm?"
  37,93,faqbl ealaa alihatuhum ydrbha wykssirha biadih alymny; liuthabit liqawmih khataan ebadthm lha
  37,94,faqblu 'iilayh yaedun msreyn ghadbyn
  37,95,"flqyhm 'iibrahim bthbat qayla kayf taebudun asnamana tnhtwnha antm, wtsnewnha baydykm, wttrkwn eibadat rabakum aladhi khlqkm, wakhalaq emlkm?"
  37,96,"flqyhm 'iibrahim bthbat qayla kayf taebudun asnamana tnhtwnha antm, wtsnewnha baydykm, wttrkwn eibadat rabakum aladhi khlqkm, wakhalaq emlkm?"
  37,97,"(flma qamat ealayhim alhujat lajawuu 'iilaa alqw) wqalu: abnuu lah bnyanana wamlwwh htbana, thuma alqwh fyh"
  37,98,"fa'arad qawm 'iibrahim bih kydana l'ihlakh, fajaealnahum almqhwryn almghlwbyn, wrdd allah kaydahum fi nhwrhm, wajaeal alnnar ealaa 'iibrahim brdana wslamana"
  37,99,"wqal 'ibrahym: 'iiniy muhajir 'iilaa rabiy min balad qawmi 'iilaa hayth 'atamakan min eibadat rby; fa'iinah sydlny ealaa alkhayr fi diniin wdnyay. rabi aetny wldana salhana"
  37,100,"wqal 'ibrahym: 'iiniy muhajir 'iilaa rabiy min balad qawmi 'iilaa hayth 'atamakan min eibadat rby; fa'iinah sydlny ealaa alkhayr fi diniin wdnyay. rabi aetny wldana salhana"
  37,101,"fajbna lah dewth, wbshsharnah bighulam hlym, ay: yakun hlymana fi kbrh, wahu 'ismaeyl"
  37,102,"flma kabir 'iismaeil wmsha mae 'abih qal lah abwh: 'iiniy 'araa fi almanam 'aniy adhbhk, fama rayk? (wrwya al'anbia' hq) faqal 'iismaeil murdyana rbh, barrana bwaldh, meynana lah ealaa taeat allh: amd ma amrk allah bih min dhbhy, satajiduni -'in sha' allh- sabrana tayeana mhtsbana"
  37,103,"flma astslma li'amr allah wanqada lh, wa'alqaa 'iibrahim aibnih ealaa jbynh -whw janib aljbht- ealaa alard; lydhbhh"
  37,104,"wnadyna 'iibrahim fi tilk alhalat alesybt: 'an ya 'ibrahym, qad felt ma 'umrt bih wsaddaqt rwyak, 'iinaa kama jzynak ealaa tsdyqk najzi aladhin 'ahsanuu mthlk, fnkhllishm min alshdayd fi aldunya walakhrt"
  37,105,"wnadyna 'iibrahim fi tilk alhalat alesybt: 'an ya 'ibrahym, qad felt ma 'umrt bih wsaddaqt rwyak, 'iinaa kama jzynak ealaa tsdyqk najzi aladhin 'ahsanuu mthlk, fnkhllishm min alshdayd fi aldunya walakhrt"
  37,106,'in al'amr bidhibh abnak hu alabtla' alshaq aldhy aban ean sidq 'iymank
  37,107,"wastnqdhna 'ismaeyl, fajaealna badilaan eanh kbshana ezymana"
  37,108,wabqyna li'iibrahim thna'an hsnana fi al'umam bedh
  37,109,"thyt li'iibrahim min eind allh, wdea' lah balslamt min kuli aft"
  37,110,"kma jzyna 'iibrahim ealaa taeth lana wamtthalh amrna, najzi almuhsinin min ebadna"
  37,111,'iinah min eibadina almuminin aladhin aetau aleubudiat hqha
  37,112,"wbshsharna 'iibrahim biwaladih 'iishaq nbyana min alsalhyn; jaza'an lah ealaa sabrah wrdah bi'amr rbh, wtaeth lh"
  37,113,"wanzlna ealayhima albrk. wmin dhuriyatihima man hu mtye lrbh, muhsin lnfsh, wman hu zalim laha zlmana byinana bkfrh wmesyth"
  37,114,"wlqd mnnna ealaa musaa waharun balnbwt walrsalt, wanajaynahuma waqawmahuma min alghrq, wama kanuu fih min ebwdyt wmadhllat"
  37,115,"wlqd mnnna ealaa musaa waharun balnbwt walrsalt, wanajaynahuma waqawmahuma min alghrq, wama kanuu fih min ebwdyt wmadhllat"
  37,116,"wnsrnahm, fakanat lahum aleizat walnsrt walghlbt ealaa fireawn walh"
  37,117,"watynahma altawrat albynt, wahadaynahuma altariq almustaqim aldhy la aewjaj fyh, wahu al'islam din allah aladhi abteth bih anbya'h, wabqyna lahuma thna'an hsnana wdhkrana jamilana fymn bedhma"
  37,118,"watynahma altawrat albynt, wahadaynahuma altariq almustaqim aldhy la aewjaj fyh, wahu al'islam din allah aladhi abteth bih anbya'h, wabqyna lahuma thna'an hsnana wdhkrana jamilana fymn bedhma"
  37,119,"watynahma altawrat albynt, wahadaynahuma altariq almustaqim aldhy la aewjaj fyh, wahu al'islam din allah aladhi abteth bih anbya'h, wabqyna lahuma thna'an hsnana wdhkrana jamilana fymn bedhma"
  37,120,"thyt lmwsa waharun min eind allh, wthna' wdea' lahuma balslamt min kuli aft, kama jzynahma aljaza' alhasan najzi almuhsinin min eibadina almukhlasin lana bialsidq wal'iiman waleml. 'iinahuma min eibadina alraskhyn fi al'iyman"
  37,121,"thyt lmwsa waharun min eind allh, wthna' wdea' lahuma balslamt min kuli aft, kama jzynahma aljaza' alhasan najzi almuhsinin min eibadina almukhlasin lana bialsidq wal'iiman waleml. 'iinahuma min eibadina alraskhyn fi al'iyman"
  37,122,"thyt lmwsa waharun min eind allh, wthna' wdea' lahuma balslamt min kuli aft, kama jzynahma aljaza' alhasan najzi almuhsinin min eibadina almukhlasin lana bialsidq wal'iiman waleml. 'iinahuma min eibadina alraskhyn fi al'iyman"
  37,123,"w'in eabdana 'iilyas lamin aladhin akrmnahm balnbwt walrsalt, 'iidh qal liqawmih min bani 'israyyl: ataquu allah wahdah wkhafwh, wala tushrikuu maeah ghyrh, kayf taebudun snmana, wttrkwn eibadat allah 'ahsan alkhalqyn, wahu rabakum aladhi khlqkm, wakhalaq aba'akum almadyn qblkm?"
  37,124,"w'in eabdana 'iilyas lamin aladhin akrmnahm balnbwt walrsalt, 'iidh qal liqawmih min bani 'israyyl: ataquu allah wahdah wkhafwh, wala tushrikuu maeah ghyrh, kayf taebudun snmana, wttrkwn eibadat allah 'ahsan alkhalqyn, wahu rabakum aladhi khlqkm, wakhalaq aba'akum almadyn qblkm?"
  37,125,"w'in eabdana 'iilyas lamin aladhin akrmnahm balnbwt walrsalt, 'iidh qal liqawmih min bani 'israyyl: ataquu allah wahdah wkhafwh, wala tushrikuu maeah ghyrh, kayf taebudun snmana, wttrkwn eibadat allah 'ahsan alkhalqyn, wahu rabakum aladhi khlqkm, wakhalaq aba'akum almadyn qblkm?"
  37,126,"w'in eabdana 'iilyas lamin aladhin akrmnahm balnbwt walrsalt, 'iidh qal liqawmih min bani 'israyyl: ataquu allah wahdah wkhafwh, wala tushrikuu maeah ghyrh, kayf taebudun snmana, wttrkwn eibadat allah 'ahsan alkhalqyn, wahu rabakum aladhi khlqkm, wakhalaq aba'akum almadyn qblkm?"
  37,127,"fkdhb qawm 'iilyas nbyhm, flyjmenhm allah yawm alqiamat llhsab waleqab, 'iilaa eibad allah aladhin akhlsu dinahum llh, fa'iinahum najwn min edhabh"
  37,128,"fkdhb qawm 'iilyas nbyhm, flyjmenhm allah yawm alqiamat llhsab waleqab, 'iilaa eibad allah aladhin akhlsu dinahum llh, fa'iinahum najwn min edhabh"
  37,129,"wajaealna l'ilyas thna'an jamilaan fi al'umam baedah. tahiatan min allh, wthna' ealaa 'ilyas. wakama jzyna 'iilyas aljaza' alhasan ealaa taeth, najzi almuhsinin min eibadina almwmnyn. 'iinah min eibad allah almuminin almukhlasin lah aleamilin bawamrh"
  37,130,"wjelna l'ilyas thna'an jamilaan fi al'umam baedah. tahiatan min allh, wthna' ealaa 'ilyas. wakama jzyna 'iilyas aljaza' alhasan ealaa taeth, najzi almuhsinin min eibadina almwmnyn. 'iinah min eibad allah almuminin almukhlasin lah aleamilin bawamrh"
  37,131,"wjelna l'ilyas thna'an jamilaan fi al'umam baedah. tahiatan min allh, wthna' ealaa 'ilyas. wakama jzyna 'iilyas aljaza' alhasan ealaa taeth, najzi almuhsinin min eibadina almwmnyn. 'iinah min eibad allah almuminin almukhlasin lah aleamilin bawamrh"
  37,132,"wjelna l'ilyas thna'an jamilaan fi al'umam baedah. tahiatan min allh, wthna' ealaa 'ilyas. wakama jzyna 'iilyas aljaza' alhasan ealaa taeth, najzi almuhsinin min eibadina almwmnyn. 'iinah min eibad allah almuminin almukhlasin lah aleamilin bawamrh"
  37,133,"w'in eabdana lwtana astfynah, fajaealnah min almrslyn, 'iidh najaynah wa'ahlah 'ajmaein min aledhab, 'iilaa ejwzana harimt, hi zwjth, hlkt mae aladhin hlku min qawmaha lkfrha"
  37,134,"w'in eabdana lwtana astfynah, fajaealnah min almrslyn, 'iidh najaynah wa'ahlah 'ajmaein min aledhab, 'iilaa ejwzana harimt, hi zwjth, hlkt mae aladhin hlku min qawmaha lkfrha"
  37,135,"w'in eabdana lwtana astfynah, fajaealnah min almrslyn, 'iidh najaynah wa'ahlah 'ajmaein min aledhab, 'iilaa ejwzana harimt, hi zwjth, hlkt mae aladhin hlku min qawmaha lkfrha"
  37,136,thm 'ahlakna albaqin almukadhibin min qwmh
  37,137,"w'inkm -ya 'ahl \"mk\"- latamuruwn fi asfarkm ealaa manazil qawm lut watharahum waqt alsbah, wtmrwn ealayha lyla. 'afala teqlwn, ftkhafu 'an yusibakum mithl ma asabhm?"
  37,138,"wa'iinakum -ya 'ahl \"mk\"- latamuruwn fi asfarkm ealaa manazil qawm lut watharahum waqt alsbah, wtmrwn ealayha lyla. 'afala teqlwn, ftkhafu 'an yusibakum mithl ma asabhm?"
  37,139,"w'in eabdana yunis astafaynah wajaealnah min almrslyn, 'iidh harab min bldh ghadbana ealaa qwmh, wrkb safinat mmlw't rkabana wamtet"
  37,140,"w'in eabdana yunis astafaynah wajaealnah min almrslyn, 'iidh harab min bldh ghadbana ealaa qwmh, wrkb safinat mmlw't rkabana wamtet"
  37,141,"wahatt biha al'amwaj alezymt, faqtre rukkab alsafinat ltkhfyf alhmwlt khawf alghrq, fakan yunis min almghlwbyn"
  37,142,"f'ulqy fi albhr, fabtleh alhwt, wayunus ealayh alslam at bima yulam elyh"
  37,143,"flwla ma tqddam lah min kathrat alebadt waleamal alsaalih qabl wuqueih fi batan alhwt, wtsbyhh, wahu fi batan alhut bqwlh: {la 'iilah 'iila 'ant subhanak 'inni kunt min alzzalimin (21:87)}, lmkth fi batan alhwt, wasar lah qbrana 'iilaa yawm alqyamt"
  37,144,"flwla ma tqddam lah min kathrat alebadt waleamal alsaalih qabl wuqueih fi batan alhwt, wtsbyhh, wahu fi batan alhut bqwlh: {la 'iilah 'iila 'ant subhanak 'inni kunt min alzzalimin (21:87)}, lmkth fi batan alhwt, wasar lah qbrana 'iilaa yawm alqyamt"